A place where kanha becomes shri nath jii 🥺🙏🏻इस जगह पर मेरा पूरा दिल बसता है 🌸🦚❤️

📍Dwarkadhish 
This place is where science meets religion and offers compelling evidence. Did you know that one of the dwarkas is also underwater? It’s fascinating to think that loard krishna spent his adulthood and entire life here , isn’t it?

The beauty of this place is mesmerising,but remember,no cameras,phone ,or any other electronic gadgets are allowed inside.However,you can capture stunning photos outside the premises 🦚🌸. I bet you,if you don’t fall in love here , I don’t know where you will .

Pro tip :-Make sure you attend the aarti and gaze into his eyes its sure to make you fall in love 😍

latestPosts.caption:
Dear Indore:)
You were never just a place on a map—you were a feeling, a rhythm, a chapter of life that changed me.Thank you for your streets that became familiar paths, for the sunsets that painted my evenings, and for the quiet corners that held my thoughts. Thank you for the noise, the chaos, the beauty, and the unexpected peace.You gave me people I’ll never forget, moments that shaped who I am, and a thousand memories I didn’t know I needed.
It’s hard to leave, but it’s harder to forget.
This isn’t just goodbye—it’s “see you again,” somewhere down the road.
With all my heart,
Cookieee♥️
Sunset’s cute, but have you seen me?”
